ize=1> Hellooo Everyone,<br>
<br>
I had to get this off my chest.  Aftter I saw this board and read the posts I was very impressed and I thought this was a good way to exchange info.  So I decided to go check out other boards. (Sorry Rebo but I had too)  What I found at the other boards I went too was most disturbing.  I went to a message about soloing I solo a lot for exp and feel that Mages are great at it.  Well this poster listed all the good solo classes and of course he did'nt mention Mages.  Why??  He said the Wizard are a great class to solo but Mages were just not up too the task!!!!  This disturbed me, so I went to eqvault and saw that there was a Mage forum there.  What I read there was even worse everyone was complaining that our class sucks.  We have no unique abilities or spells they said.  Our summing spells were a joke they said.  We are the least powerful class they said!!!!!   And these are the Mages complaining.  SO I left that forum and went too another Mage forum, much like this one.  (but not as good)  I saw there was a disscussion of posts about Mages and groups.  When I read that I was completely discusted.  The posts mainly were from mages and they all were complaining about how we had nothing too offer groups?!?  How everytime they joined a group they were turned away for being a Mage or were not allowed to summon a pet because &quot;it ate up too much exp&quot;.  SO in the past too days I have read many posts on various boards and forums.  What I got from them  is that Mages are no good at solo or in a group.  That our spells are weak and our summoning ability is usless.  This makes me sick!!  Please someone post and tell me we are a great class.  I know my Lvl 18 mage rocks!! How come no one else seems to aprieciate us??  Sorry this is so long but I had too tell someone about what is being said about us.  Thanks for reading this (you are very paticient).  <br>
<br>
Riplin (Gnome Mage LVL 1<img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><br>
<br>
