Keep in mind, people tend to do a lot of whining about thier class... especially on everquest.com.<br>
<br>
I've played a Warrior to 16th, a Druid to 24th and a Magician to 31st.  Magicians Rock! (though I still miss SoW. Oh well, I hang out regularly with a Druid!).  <br>
<br>
